Hi there :)

I'm currently working on my bachelor's thesis in which I proof that creating WebComponents using [OrbitDB](https://github.com/orbitdb/orbit-db/blob/master/GUIDE.md) is possible. OrbitDB uses ipfs and its experimental pubsub feature, including the transport over WebSockets.

```
